column2: PREPARE FOR INSERTION. WATCH OUT FOR THE SNIPER IN THE SOUTH. KEEP YOUR HEADS DOWN AND MOVE, FIRE, MOVE. MAKE ME PROUD.
DELTA LEADER REPORTING, THE ENEMY HELO IS DOWN. I REPEAT THE ENEMY HELICOPTER IS DOWN. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALL FORCES. ALL RUSSIANS ARE EITHER DEAD OR FLEEING, GOOD JOB. OVER.
